ada to be running neck and neck with his closest challenger, Prince Abubakar Audu, the candidate of the All Progressives Congress, APC. November 22, 2015 In "News" ...Sen Diri votes decries allege hijack of materials in some parts of the state By Emem Idio, Yenegoa The candidate of the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, Senator Douye Diri and his wife Gloria have cast their vote in Sampou Community of Kolokuma /Opokuma Local Government Area. The PDP candidate voted… November 16, 2019 In "News"